gland credited with?

00:00:43.880 --> 00:00:47.600 align:middle line:84%
We're speaking with Rabbi Joel
Bakst today, a Jewish scholar,

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:49.570 align:middle line:84%
regarding his belief
that the Torah is

00:00:49.570 --> 00:00:52.310 align:middle line:84%
the gateway to
understanding the pineal

00:00:52.310 --> 00:00:54.760 align:middle line:84%
and our connection
with divine source.

00:00:54.760 --> 00:00:55.600 align:middle line:90%
Welcome.

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:56.320 align:middle line:90%
>>JOEL BAKST: Thank you, Regina.

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:57.736 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: This
will be interesting

00:00:57.736 --> 00:01:00.250 align:middle line:84%
