us have not been--

00:01:03.650 --> 00:01:07.340 align:middle line:84%
unless you're a Jewish scholar--
have been exposed to before.

00:01:07.340 --> 00:01:08.825 align:middle line:84%
So this is going
to be fun for us.

00:01:08.825 --> 00:01:10.200 align:middle line:84%
>>BAKST: Yes, I
expect there will

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:12.000 align:middle line:90%
